ry_id>59106</s:story_id></item><item><title>West Virginia Drops Game Two to TCU</title><link>https://wvusports.com/news/2026/5/15/baseball-west-virginia-drops-game-two-to-tcu</link><guid>https://wvusports.com/news/2026/5/15/baseball-west-virginia-drops-game-two-to-tcu</guid><category>Baseball</category><description><![CDATA[<img alt="Maxx Yehl throws a pitch against TCU" src="https://admin.wvusports.com/common/controls/image_handler.aspx?thumb_prefix=rp_primary&image_path=/images/2026/5/15/baseball5-15.jpg" /><br /><br />MORGANTOWN, W.Va. – The No. 9 West Virginia University baseball team fell to TCU, 4-0, Friday night at Kendrick Family Ballpark. The Mountaineers fall to 36-13 and 20-9 in the Big 12 while the Horned Frogs improve to 33-19 and 17-12 in league play.]]></description><media:thumbnail url="https://admin.wvusports.com/common/controls/image_handler.aspx?thumb_prefix=rp_system&amp;image_path=/images/2026/5/15/baseball5-15.jpg" /><media:content url="https://admin.wvusports.com/common/controls/image_handler.aspx?thumb_prefix=rp_primary&amp;image_path=/images/2026/5/15/baseball5-15.jpg"><media:title>Maxx Yehl throws a pitch against TCU</media:title></media:content><enclosure url="https://admin.wvusports.com/common/controls/image_handler.aspx?thumb_prefix=rp_primary&amp;image_path=/images/2026/5/15/baseball5-15.jpg" length="1" type="image/jpg" /><pubDate>Fri, 15 May 2026 22:58:00 EST</pubDate><s:sport_id>1</s:sport_id><s:story_id>59105</s:story_id></item><item><title>Saturday's Game Against TCU Moved Up</title><link>https://wvusports.com/news/2026/5/15/baseball-saturdays-game-against-tcu-moved-up</link><guid>https://wvusports.com/news/2026/5/15/baseball-saturdays-game-against-tcu-moved-up</guid><category>Baseball</category><description><![CDATA[<img alt="Schedule Update vs TCU graphic showing first pitch is now at noon" src="https://admin.wvusports.com/common/controls/image_handler.aspx?thumb_prefix=rp_primary&image_path=/images/2026/5/15/1920x1080TCU.jpg" /><